{"tid":1161053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突遭人從後起飛腳偷襲 71歲阿諾舒華辛力加仆向前","createTime":"2019-05-19T01:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T08:26:46.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7f571bca4bda31d0703c538f94dce9ea5ac9306d","tid":1161053,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T01:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190519/large/1558197812_bc50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190519%2Flarge%2F1558197812_bc50.jpg&h=919b1d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190519/large/1558197988_510a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190519%2Flarge%2F1558197988_510a.jpg&h=83167708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷李活影星阿諾舒華辛力加(Arnold Schwarzenegger)在南非一間體育館內與一群影迷傾談和自拍合照時，突遭一名男子從後起飛腳踢倒，幸而沒有受傷，該男子事後被帶走。<br />\n阿諾當時正在南非出席一項活動，與一群民眾包括影迷傾談和自拍，一名男子突然從後衝前，飛身用腳踢向他背部，71歲的阿諾一度失去重心仆前，但他事後在Twitter發文表示自己無恙，叮囑大家不用擔心。他說：「我當時以為有人在後面推撞，這是經常發生的事，後來像大家一樣看到片段才知道有人踢我，我很慶幸那笨蛋沒有妨礙我snapchat。」<br />\n施襲男子事後被人拖走，其他人則一湧上前察看阿諾有否受傷，阿諾向旁人微笑和握手，之後在大批保安簇擁下離開。由於事出突然，又有不少小童在場，不少人都發出驚呼聲，一名小孩更似乎被嚇到，要大人安慰。<br />\n活動負責人表示施襲男子「是慣犯，以往亦曾做出同樣行為」。阿諾表示不會向他提控，周日將如期繼續活動。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》/美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190519/59616654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190519%2F59616654&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPdAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=9a373517\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190519%2F59616654&h=0878296b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190519/59616654</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線咁樣飛踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffbcf3c036673662bfc8b4d2dc63e6c25137fae9","tid":1161053,"uid":52763,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T01:42:47.000Z","msg":"未來戰士都夠膽踢"},{"pid":"d3a8682424baaf63740484b2eb2f81ad5073d29b","tid":1161053,"uid":198223,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T01:45:28.000Z","msg":"慣犯? 會有人有d 咁既喜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2fdfc938c69c80b08b991a6a5d11057b069713","tid":1161053,"uid":54721,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T01:58:17.000Z","msg":"71歲都咁硬淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f2ceaabcedc4d32bc77dea661ea5783d761d2f","tid":1161053,"uid":66395,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:13:39.000Z","msg":"連登仔 : 健身無撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b430fb0e4b5367fa2cc7becffbbe889859c3f656","tid":1161053,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:17:12.000Z","msg":"打阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e17371c80aa38ff4fbdd81f359a2f7fa9e081e9","tid":1161053,"uid":104446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:22:54.000Z","msg":"佢回應得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾人咁踢都只係覺得推撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2d4f345e3076c9e3cb733f5911581ebf74e49f","tid":1161053,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T02:37:13.000Z","msg":"阿諾個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7qwKVf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7qwKVf.jpg&h=8cd09238&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff164e9eebe13a878c10faedfc5b9b6bb2aa2988","tid":1161053,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e2d4f345e3076c9e3cb733f5911581ebf74e49f","tid":1161053,"u